'We have found many of our folk lying slain as they fled thither,'
'Erkenbrand!'
'Help now to repair the evil in which you have joined,'
's Gate, if he has not already perished.'
'Erkenbrand!'
'and afterwards you shall take an oath never again to pass the Fords of Isen in arms, nor to march with the enemies of Men; and then you shall go free back to your land. For you have been deluded by Saruman. Many of you have got death as the reward of your trust in him; but had you conquered, little better would your wages have been.'
